paragraphs.text:
%jdbc

from phillycrime 
where text_general_code like '%Assault%' 
group by dispatch_date, text_general_code
order by count(*) desc

%jdbc

select count(*) as NumberOfCrimes, dispatch_date, text_general_code
from phillycrime 
group by dispatch_date, text_general_code
order by dispatch_date desc

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc

select count(*) as NumberOfCrimes, dispatch_date, text_general_code
from phillycrime 
Where text_general_code like '%Assault%'  or
text_general_code like '%Robbery Firearm%' or text_general_code like '%Rape%'
group by dispatch_date, text_general_code

paragraphs.text:
%jdbc

select count(*) as NumberOfCrimes, dispatch_date, text_general_code
from phillycrime 
Where text_general_code like '%Assault%'  or
text_general_code like '%Robbery Firearm%' or text_general_code like '%Rape%'
group by dispatch_date, text_general_code
Having count(*) > 50
order by dispatch_date desc

%jdbc

select count(*) as NumberOfCrimes, dispatch_date, text_general_code
from phillycrime 
Where dispatch_date like '2019-%'
group by dispatch_date, text_general_code
order by  count(*) desc
